#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "thag5.9:4.1"
msgid "5.9. Vijitasenattheragāthā"
msgstr ""

#. </h1></div><blockquote class="gatha"><p><a class="sc" id="1"></a><a
#. class="verse-num-sc" id="verse-num-sc355"></a><a class="verse-num-pts"
#. id="verse-num-pts355"></a>
msgctxt "thag5.9:5.1"
msgid "“Olaggessāmi te citta,"
msgstr "I’ll cage you, mind,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag5.9:5.2"
msgid "āṇidvāreva hatthinaṃ;"
msgstr "Like an elephant in a stockade."

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag5.9:5.3"
msgid "Na taṃ pāpe niyojessaṃ,"
msgstr "Born of the flesh, that net of sensual pleasures,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag5.9:5.4"
msgid "<span class=\"var\" title=\"kāmajālaṃ (s2, s3)\" id=\"note196\">kāmajāla</span> <span class=\"var\" title=\"sariraja (bj) | sarīrajaṃ (s2, s3, mr)\" id=\"note197\">sarīraja</span>."
msgstr "I won’t urge you to do bad."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="2"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc356"></a><a class="verse-num-pts"
#. id="verse-num-pts356"></a><a class="pts" id="pts40"></a>
msgctxt "thag5.9:6.1"
msgid "Tvaṃ olaggo na gacchasi,"
msgstr "Caged, you won’t escape,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag5.9:6.2"
msgid "Dvāravivaraṃ gajova alabhanto;"
msgstr "Like an elephant who can’t find an open gate."

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag5.9:6.3"
msgid "Na ca cittakali punappunaṃ,"
msgstr "Demon-mind, you won’t wander again and again,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag5.9:6.4"
msgid "<span class=\"var\" title=\"pasahaṃ (bj, s2, s3, pts1-2)\" id=\"note198\">Pasakka</span> pāparato carissasi."
msgstr "Bullying, and loving to do bad."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="3"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc357"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts357"></a>
msgctxt "thag5.9:7.1"
msgid "Yathā kuñjaraṃ adantaṃ,"
msgstr "Just as a strong trainer with a hook,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag5.9:7.2"
msgid "Navaggahamaṅkusaggaho;"
msgstr "Takes a wild, newly captured elephant"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag5.9:7.3"
msgid "Balavā āvatteti akāmaṃ,"
msgstr "And wins it over against its will,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag5.9:7.4"
msgid "Evaṃ āvattayissaṃ taṃ."
msgstr "So I’ll win you over."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="4"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc358"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts358"></a>
msgctxt "thag5.9:8.1"
msgid "Yathā varahayadamakusalo,"
msgstr "Just as a fine charioteer, skilled in the taming"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag5.9:8.2"
msgid "Sārathi pavaro dameti ājaññaṃ;"
msgstr "Of fine horses, tames a thoroughbred,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag5.9:8.3"
msgid "Evaṃ damayissaṃ taṃ,"
msgstr "So I’ll tame you,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag5.9:8.4"
msgid "Patiṭṭhito pañcasu balesu."
msgstr "Firmly established in the five powers."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="5"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc359"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts359"></a>
msgctxt "thag5.9:9.1"
msgid "Satiyā taṃ nibandhissaṃ,"
msgstr "I’ll bind you with mindfulness,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag5.9:9.2"
msgid "<span class=\"var\" title=\"payatatto vo dapessāmi (bj, pts2) | payatatto te damissāmi (s2, s3) | payatatto vo damessāmi (pts1)\" id=\"note199\">Payutto te damessāmi</span>;"
msgstr "I’m committed to taming you;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag5.9:9.3"
msgid "Vīriyadhuraniggahito,"
msgstr "Restrained by harnessed energy,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag5.9:9.4"
msgid "Na yito dūraṃ gamissase cittā”ti."
msgstr "Mind, you won’t go far from here."

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
